possession-charge-2624942">于 2019 年因持有武器被捕，并被判处四年监禁</a>。然而，卡普里<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-wayne-kodak-black-president-trump-considering-pardoning-2851925">后来被美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普赦免。</a></p><p>柯达·布莱克<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kodak-black-arrested-on-drug-charges-in-california-3556335">(Kodak Black) 在加州因毒品指控被捕的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 Sum 41 的 Deryck Whibley 讲述了肺炎后“可怕”的住院治疗https://www.nme.com/news/music/sum-41s-deryck-whibley-opens-up-about-scary-hospitalise-following-pneumonia-3556331?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=sum-41s-deryck-惠布利公开了肺炎后可怕的住院治疗Anagricel DuranFri, 08 Dec 2023 20:54:21 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop-punkRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3556331 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sum-41-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Sum 41 乐队的 Deryck Whibley 于 2022 年 10 月 21 日在英国伦敦亚历山德拉宫举行的“Does This Look All Killer No Filler”巡演中进行表演。 （摄影：Burak Cingi/Redferns）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sum-41-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sum-41-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sum-41-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sum-41-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sum-41-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sum-41-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “当医生如此担心时，这对我来说是最可怕的。我能感觉到我的心脏很难受”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sum-41s-deryck-whibley-opens-up-about-scary-hospitalisation-following-pneumonia-3556331">Sum 41 后的 Deryck Whibley 谈到了</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现肺炎后的“可怕”住院治疗。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sum-41-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Sum 41 乐队的 Deryck Whibley 于 2022 年 10 月 21 日在英国伦敦亚历山德拉宫举行的“Does This Look All Killer No Filler”巡演中进行表演。 （摄影：Burak Cingi/Redferns）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sum-41-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Sum-41-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-cont